en_125283_0	A 68-year-old man with two locally made weapons was arrested by the Special Task Force, the police said.
en_125283_1	He was arrested near a school in Kuliyapitiya- Anukkana.
en_125283_2	Police said that the weapons were found when he was checked as he was riding his motorbike.
en_125283_3	The suspect will be produced before the Kuliyapitiya Magistrate Courts today
